Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.79,0:00:04.19,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.97,0:00:05.85,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We'll all do it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.52,0:00:10.36,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.08,0:00:13.40,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's better together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:20.24,Saku-main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Please give us your signature!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.24,0:00:22.70,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Please lend your support!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.78,0:00:24.75,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Please help us gather signatures \Nto keep Sakura Hall open!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.70,0:00:26.58,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Please give us your signature!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.75,0:00:25.66,Saku-overlap,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.66,0:00:26.58,Saku-overlap,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Please give us your support!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.00,0:00:29.29,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Please help us gather signatures!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.29,0:00:30.09,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:31.13,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.13,0:00:32.81,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.81,0:00:34.76,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you want to \Ngive us your signature!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:34.34,Saku-overlap,STUDENTS,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.34,0:00:35.63,Saku-overlap,STUDENTS,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.13,0:00:37.85,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.93,0:00:40.35,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:42.89,Saku-main,VENDOR,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Sakura Hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.89,0:00:44.18,Saku-main,WOMAN,0000,0000,0000,,We support you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:46.52,Saku-main,VENDOR,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata-kun, give it your best shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.52,0:00:48.48,Saku-main,VENDOR,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:49.86,Saku-main,VENDOR,0000,0000,0000,,Guts! It takes guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.44,0:00:52.98,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow's formation has been decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.98,0:00:55.28,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'm on a school trip...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:00:55.94,Saku-overlap,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,How's this, kouhai-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.94,0:00:57.70,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Great. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.86,0:01:00.32,Saku-main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,Please give us your support!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.83,0:01:01.62,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.24,0:01:03.54,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:05.50,Saku-main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.08,0:01:09.92,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:13.71,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.71,0:01:15.96,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd have to come back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.96,0:01:17.88,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Ayano, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.88,0:01:18.59,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.60,0:01:27.52,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You finally got a cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:29.16,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Mashiron!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.16,0:01:31.15,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,That's great, Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:33.36,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.94,0:01:35.74,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.24,0:01:38.57,Saku-overlap,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, it's the last spurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:38.57,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We all knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.59,0:01:44.82,Sign,CALENDAR,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun's Game Title Screening\NLast Day to Gather Signatures | Graduation Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.82,0:01:40.20,Saku-overlap,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow's our last day!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.49,0:01:44.83,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,There were only a few more days \Nwe could spend like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:41.95,Saku-overlap,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Show some spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:44.83,Saku-overlap,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,All together, everyone. Ready, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.08,0:01:47.66,Saku-main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit!
