Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.49,0:03:21.19,Saku-main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,Please show your support!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.19,0:03:22.93,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Please help us gather signatures!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:24.92,Saku-main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,Please show your support!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.92,0:03:27.11,Saku-main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,Please show your support!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:28.93,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We can't get any.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.14,0:03:47.20,Saku-main,SHIHO,0000,0000,0000,,What are you painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:49.61,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:54.49,Saku-main,SHIHO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:04.18,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Total: 335 People
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.14,0:04:16.81,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Game Title Screening
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.66,0:04:39.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:43.60,Saku-main,TEACHER,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:49.67,Saku-main,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,What? What's wrong with Nanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:51.81,Saku-main,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. She seems to be crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:58.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, Aoyama doesn't \Nseem to be feeling well,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:05:00.29,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll take her to the nurse's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:02.53,Saku-main,TEACHER,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay, please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:06.70,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.30,0:05:22.08,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:24.88,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You should go back to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:26.17,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:32.80,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Call me if you need anything, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:34.34,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Promise you'll call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.58,0:06:02.25,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Incoming Call\NFujisawa Kazuki
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:07.79,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.48,0:06:10.63,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for all your hard work. It's Fujisawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:12.26,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for all your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.36,0:06:15.13,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:16.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.04,0:06:19.02,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,The game title screening \Nmeeting is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:24.11,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, we didn't \Nmake it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:32.48,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.42,0:06:34.03,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:34.62,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.88,0:06:39.87,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,It turns out a second music game...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:42.33,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,had been submitted to\N the game title screening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:42.33,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Rhythm Battler
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:45.79,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I can't give details,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.79,0:06:48.08,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but it uses songs from \Na popular musical anime...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.08,0:06:52.14,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and Vocaloid songs \Npopular on the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.19,0:06:57.01,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's a simple game following the \Nsystem of previous music games,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.69,0:07:01.48,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but that title passed the \Nscreening meeting this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:05.64,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that they don't \Nneed two music games?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:08.86,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that would be the main reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:11.65,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's... That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:15.90,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,If I had moved through our \Nmeetings faster and submitted it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.25,0:07:18.54,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to the game title screening sooner...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:22.62,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm grateful for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.47,0:07:26.37,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You made time for me\N even on your weekends off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:30.01,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I was able \Nto work on my pitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.86,0:07:32.84,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I learned a lot from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:37.18,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be so reasonable about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:41.77,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Your future is decided by \Nforces beyond your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:43.88,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard you work,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.32,0:07:45.60,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,there are things you cannot change.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:47.77,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.49,0:07:50.19,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to accept \Nthings so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:55.28,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,But the world is full of such unfairness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:07:59.95,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you more information...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:02.49,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,about the game title screening \Nmeeting at a later date.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:03.95,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:07.25,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything you'd \Nlike to ask me right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.35,0:08:12.21,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What did you think of our pitch?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:14.29,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'd like to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.94,0:08:19.42,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,As a creator, I wanted \Nto create a prototype.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.23,0:08:23.82,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,As a user, I wanted to \Ntry playing it once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.49,0:08:27.59,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,It could have become \Nan interesting game,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:29.78,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but with the wrong balance,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:33.15,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,it could also have been a \Nflat and terrible game.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.79,0:08:35.94,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.67,0:08:38.48,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a little better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.42,0:08:41.45,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call you again later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.36,0:09:03.68,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,This is too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.28,0:09:06.65,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:13.52,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.29,0:09:15.53,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:17.81,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,A different music game?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:21.12,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I can do about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.63,0:09:26.12,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:31.91,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:44.18,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Akasaka Ryunosuke\NNo Subject\NHow's Ponytail doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:49.66,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Akasaka Ryunosuke\NShe said she was all right, \Nso I left her to rest in the nurse's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.66,0:09:50.65,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Sending
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:59.32,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Message Received\NAkasaka Ryunosuke
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:06.21,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,What are you? Stupid?\NSomeone who's all right wouldn't cry like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.51,0:10:11.70,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:15.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,He's so right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:34.60,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:09.64,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:19.19,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.60,0:11:20.95,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.19,0:11:24.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.69,0:11:27.76,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I was happy you worked so hard \Nfor Sakura Hall, for Shiina,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.28,0:11:31.25,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,for Misaki-senpai and Jin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.78,0:11:36.38,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I was really happy you cared \Nso much about Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:41.86,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't have to sacrifice \Nyourself to this extent!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.12,0:11:42.90,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:46.27,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:49.71,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk about me like \NI'm some kind of saint.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.59,0:11:52.45,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.89,0:11:56.11,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I've been making all kinds of excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:58.50,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,"Sakura Hall is in trouble."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.02,0:12:01.28,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,"I have to think of Mashiro's feelings."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:04.92,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,"I won't cry in front of \NKamiigusa-senpai and Mitaka-senpai."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.01,0:12:07.73,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,They're all excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.90,0:12:09.85,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:13.01,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,afraid the last two \Nyears would go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:15.46,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I was so afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:19.35,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I prepared suitable \Nexcuses for Sakura Hall,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:22.05,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,for Mashiro, and for Kamiigusa-senpai \Nand Mitaka-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:27.39,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I did it so I wouldn't get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.63,0:12:29.64,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.42,0:12:34.64,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I've only used excuses \Nto pretend I'm not hurting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:36.94,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that makes you happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.14,0:12:38.82,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't kindness at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.73,0:12:42.75,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:48.83,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It was something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:51.41,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It had to be something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.36,0:12:54.36,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.36,0:12:57.26,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I've been able \Nto work hard for this long.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:13:00.74,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Because of you, I've managed \Nto keep canvassing for signatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.74,0:13:02.13,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you, Aoyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:04.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't have to try \Nso hard anymore, Aoyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.62,0:13:05.80,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:06.82,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.82,0:13:07.89,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It does!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:10.56,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Enough already! Don't think \Nof anything else anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:12.02,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.30,0:13:14.41,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay! That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:17.16,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Stare the results of \Nyour audition in the face!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:18.37,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run from it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.51,0:13:22.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll listen to everything \Nyou have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.86,0:13:30.31,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What about my two years?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:32.04,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I've been patient this whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:36.75,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,When my friends went to karaoke \Nor went shopping, I had work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:41.54,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I endured all of it so I wouldn't \Nregret playing around or slacking off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.29,0:13:43.25,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.79,0:13:45.61,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I even cut back on how much I spent...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:48.18,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I know. I know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.50,0:13:51.39,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to have fun, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:54.37,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I gave it everything I had, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:55.70,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:58.40,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,But it's pointless! There's no point!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:14:01.16,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,If I fail the audition, \Nit's not worth anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.16,0:14:02.40,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:05.38,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me. Tell me why, Kanda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.85,0:14:07.92,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What were those two years worth?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.92,0:14:08.91,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Why wasn't it me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.69,0:14:11.41,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Why wasn't I good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.69,0:14:16.46,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You worked hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.86,0:14:18.77,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Harder than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:22.10,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You worked harder than \Nanyone in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.10,0:14:24.40,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You really worked hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:45.46,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:49.70,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,My face looks grody. Don't stare.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:51.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Grody?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:52.52,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It means I look gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.86,0:14:54.70,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.82,0:14:56.08,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,If anything, you're cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:56.64,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.24,0:14:59.50,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, sorry! That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.41,0:15:03.52,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You had me worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.83,0:15:06.59,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,If you feel well enough to flirt, \NI guess you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:07.63,Saku-main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:15.76,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,37.3 degrees. You've got a slight fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:21.53,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Here, your medicine. \NTake this, and get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:23.11,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,But the signatures...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.35,0:15:25.00,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the last day, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.24,0:15:29.01,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,So get some rest, and prepare \Nyourself for the last push.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:31.51,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,But kids with fevers can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.11,0:15:40.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.03,0:15:43.10,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you want him to sleep beside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:44.20,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:48.15,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really? You'll have to tell him \Nwhat you want by yourself, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.65,0:15:55.18,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Kanda-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.49,0:15:56.18,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.32,0:15:59.56,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Could you stay with me \Nuntil I fall asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.82,0:16:01.31,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay until you wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:02.77,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Just until I fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:03.48,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:05.56,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't watch me sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:08.48,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I won't know if you're \Nalseep if I don't look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.41,0:16:11.90,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. That's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.60,0:16:19.04,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:19.95,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:22.96,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, I'll start thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:26.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:28.38,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:32.42,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I just got the results of the \Ngame title screening meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:35.51,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I failed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.09,0:16:40.81,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I was only thinking of myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:45.52,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I failed, but I'm glad I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:49.94,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I failed the title screening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:52.57,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.21,0:16:54.74,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not happy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:56.62,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.77,0:17:00.83,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'd cry if I let my guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.68,0:17:04.16,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I can't take it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:07.08,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I need courage to try again,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:09.44,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm a coward now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:14.05,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I can't try again so soon, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.87,0:17:17.77,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,So why don't you rest for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:19.72,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You should take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.15,0:17:24.39,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You've been working so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.01,0:17:26.90,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I think it would do you good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:31.23,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You can move forward once you've \Nregained your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.77,0:17:34.28,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.26,0:17:37.45,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You've been running this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:40.99,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine if you take a little breather.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.84,0:17:42.58,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:45.00,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.37,0:18:09.42,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:21.83,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kouhai-kun! Listen to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:25.45,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,We got 53 signatures today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:26.66,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Look, look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.24,0:18:28.17,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's not enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.38,0:18:30.08,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,We did everything we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.56,0:18:33.84,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,We're a little short of two-thirds \Nof the student body, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:35.55,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't fall a little short.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:37.30,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's not nearly enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:39.84,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't done everything I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:41.22,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't done anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.44,0:18:44.31,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why... Why didn't you wake me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:46.81,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda, don't throw a fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.22,0:18:48.94,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Ponytail did a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:52.15,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we felt sorry for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:56.36,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but we couldn't let \NAoyama-san sleep alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.17,0:18:59.79,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't she need a \Npartner-in-crime right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:02.78,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:07.20,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Is Aoyama-san still in \Nthe nurse's office?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.10,0:19:08.71,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:10.83,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's go get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:12.88,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro-chan, take care of Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.73,0:19:17.55,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.07,0:19:21.50,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,How many more?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.96,0:19:24.81,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,How many more do we need?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.27,0:19:27.52,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,A lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:30.44,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I'll get a lot, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:35.69,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.33,0:19:37.73,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.58,0:19:39.99,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You're a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:41.20,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.67,0:19:42.66,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:43.66,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.92,0:19:45.45,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:48.41,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Hall is going to be torn down,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:50.66,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and we don't have enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.73,0:19:52.79,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:05.76,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,We're home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:07.72,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's throw a "signature gathering...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:11.60,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and the night before the \Ngraduation ceremony" party!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.86,0:20:13.44,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.57,0:20:28.47,Sign,LETTER,0000,0000,0000,,Request for Character Design Work\N for Our Company's Products
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:22.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,"After seeing her fantastic \Nillustrations for Rhythm Battler,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:23.70,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,we would like to ask Shiina Mashiro-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:26.58,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to design characters for \Nour company's products..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.47,0:20:31.04,Sign,LETTER,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina Mashiro-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.06,0:20:34.37,Saku-thought,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:36.04,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Could we ask the girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.32,0:20:38.88,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,who drew this to do some \Nadditional illustrations for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.91,0:20:41.38,Saku-thought,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,It has such presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:45.30,Saku-thought,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I think including more drawings would \Nhelp us with the review board.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.66,0:20:49.93,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I get it. This is how it works...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:52.14,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.08,0:20:56.98,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The world isn't fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.79,0:21:00.82,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what ordinary people \Ntry to do, it's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.00,0:21:05.78,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much I want to \Ncatch up, it's still not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.59,0:21:10.92,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we give it everything \Nwe have, it's pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.92,0:21:12.79,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Our hard work is never rewarded!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.47,0:21:14.58,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Everything works this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.58,0:21:16.04,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Even this business with Sakura Hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:17.54,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard we tried,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:19.42,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,there was nothing we could do!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:22.17,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.09,0:21:34.89,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.58,0:21:37.73,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.47,0:23:14.74,Saku-thought,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.55,0:23:16.75,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We'll all do it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.53,0:23:32.26,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.92,0:23:35.47,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't call you by your \Nfirst name in front of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.82,0:23:40.98,NextEptitle,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(458,1)}#22 Run Through Those Sparkling Days
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.83,0:23:38.34,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Without realizing it, \Nmaybe I'm trying to be formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.79,0:23:40.98,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But that's probably because...
